{"tid":1756230,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實搞大遊行之前有樣野一定要做。","createTime":"2019-11-26T02:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T03:46:27.000Z","uid":31058,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89c42878732009f8345b36e61e1b0ff5169e0c95","tid":1756230,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>就係出份連登聯合聲明 承諾當日勇武不會進場</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n純粹和平發聲，令到政府無藉口不發出不反對通知書，藉此吸引更多和理非行出黎，重現200萬人畫面。<br />\n<br />\n經過區選，已經證明左勇武係智勇雙全，能屈能伸。我地一定要食住區選大勝氣勢，做番場好戲俾全世界睇，香港人嘅團結同埋追求民主嘅決心。<br />\n<br />\n侵侵都呼籲過想我地重現大遊行畫面，但無奈大部分和理非驚犯法之餘亦驚危險，相信呢個聲明可以消除以上兩項疑慮，聚番616 班人出黎。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"32d404e097ff5f54dc27cc74e1daf259fe8ca3d4","tid":1756230,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"0fcc1b5d22f8355004f9f749d7be2be2064c68a6","tid":1756230,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"要設死線！今次民意政府冇得唔承認唔回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d99b076bdca216ec72c908a7cda800ac6e2c5ab","tid":1756230,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe653e0b653dc0bf69313d00388ee906d52c9e87","tid":1756230,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:13:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9edec160d2e0a9543d2a57f480041efe7935a0a","tid":1756230,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"打開口牌當勇武係condom?"},{"pid":"12409c47ba76c3ed3e23f74f856c84a2d9feaac6","tid":1756230,"uid":118787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d9edec160d2e0a9543d2a57f480041efe7935a0a","tid":1756230,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"打開口牌當勇武係condom?"},"citedBy":1,"